title: Serious
alt: Not to be confused with Serious PuTTY, the Windows terminal client where everything is in Impact.
transcript:
[Cueball is standing next to a table. There is a can on the table.][The label on the can reads, "Serious Putty".][Cueball is looking at the table again.][He reaches out to touch the can. The can speaks.]
Can: Don't touch me.
